          "english": "The water temperature's still low so you're not going to swim, are you?",
          "source": {
            "type": "tatoeba",
            "id": 74360
          },
          "license": {
            "text": "CC BY 2.0 FR",
            "url": "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/fr/"
          }
        },
        {
          "japanese": "シンナーなどの常習性のある物をしてると言う事は、更正する可能性が低いと思います。",
          "kana": "しんなーなどのじょうしゅうせいのあるものをしてるということは、こうせいするかのうせいがひくいとおもいます。",
          "english": "I think that, as he's using addictive substances like thinner, the chance of rehabilitation is low.",
          "source": {
            "type": "tatoeba",
            "id": 74640
          },
          "license": {
            "text": "CC BY 2.0 FR",
            "url": "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/fr/"
          }
        }
